# ============================================================================
# Notes & Tips
# ============================================================================

# To reload config: Restart Ghostty or use keybind if configured
# To test colors: Run `msgcat --color=test`
# To see all options: ghostty --help
# To validate config: ghostty --config-check

# Alternative color schemes to try:
# - Tokyo Night
# - Nord
# - Dracula
# - Gruvbox
# - Solarized

# Recommended fonts:
# - MesloLGS Nerd Font (default, best for Powerlevel10k)
# - JetBrains Mono Nerd Font
# - Fira Code Nerd Font
# - Hack Nerd Font

# Performance tips:
# - Keep scrollback-limit reasonable (10000 is good default)
# - Use GPU rendering (auto or metal on macOS)
# - Disable background blur if performance is an issue
# - Reduce opacity to 1.0 for maximum performance
